                                課程簡介
                            

                                 
                            

                                 
                            

                                Introduction
                            





                                本課程希望能讓學生們瞭解與探討基本的說服傳播理論與原則，並將所學的理論與原則應用於說服傳播實務中。因此，本課程的內容設計將包括說服理論的介紹與探討、說服性傳播策略的基本要素，以及著名的說服性傳播個案之策略分析與研討。

《 課程簡介 -- English 》
                                The objectives of this course are to give students an opportunity to explore the basic principles of persuasion theory and to know how to apply those principles into persuasion practice. To achieve the above objectives, the contents of this course consist of systematic introduction of persuasion theories, basic elements of persuasion communication strategy, and case studies of worldwide successful persuasion cases. Moreover, this course requires students to practice analyzing persuasive communication strategies of selected cased by their own choices.











